                     <interp inst="t18200918-222-person2162" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             re-examined. When the coin was found on the prisoner, I do not recollect Cohen saying he knew them by any mark.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18200918-222-verdict1285" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200918-222-verdict1285" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Fourth Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
